00159     ------------------------------------------------------------------------ */
00160 template<class Content> void TRadioButtonList<Content>::SetPressedItem(Content content)
00161 {
00162     TRadioButtonItem<Content> *item = GetFirstItem();
00163     INT index = 0;
00164 
00165     while (item != 0) {
00166         if (item->GetContent() == content) {
00167             item->SetPressed(TRUE);
00168             GetMyModel()->SetSelectedIndex(index);
00169             return;
00170         }
00171         item = (TRadioButtonItem<Content>*)item->GetNext();
00172         index++;
00173     }
00174 
00175     ASSERT(FALSE);
00176 }   // SetPressedItem
